# Replace this with the maf-workflow URL from the Aspire dashboard Resources page.
@mafWorkflowUrl = http://localhost:5123

### Workflow snapshot
GET {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/

### Workflow status
GET {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/status

### Health check
GET {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/health

### Get workflow trace (structured event stream)
# Returns all workflow run traces with structured events including:
# - IncidentQueued: When incident is queued for processing
# - WorkflowStarted: When Squad workflow execution begins
# - SquadRuntimeDescribed: When Squad runtime loads and describes the team
# - AgentAvailable: For each agent loaded (with role, model, adapter status)
# - WorkflowCompleted/WorkflowFailed/WorkflowStopped: Final workflow status
GET {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/trace

### Trigger a simulated incident workflow
POST {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/incidents/simulate?severity=Sev2&title=Database%20latency

### Read status after triggering
GET {{mafWorkflowUrl}}/status
